#: src/components/modals/ConversationSettingsModal.tsx:351
#: src/components/modals/SpaceSettingsModal/General.tsx:335
msgid ""
"When enabled, all previous versions of edited messages will be saved. When "
"disabled, only the current edited version is kept."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, bodo shranjene vse prejšnje različice urejenih sporočil. Ko"
" je onemogočeno, se obdrži le trenutna urejena različica."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:261
msgid ""
"When enabled, other users can see when you are active. This feature is not "
"yet available."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, lahko drugi uporabniki vidijo, kdaj si aktiven. Ta funkcija"
" še ni na voljo."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:222
msgid ""
"When enabled, synchronizes your user data, Spaces, and Space keys between "
"devices. Enabling this increases metadata visibility of your account, which "
"can reveal when you have joined new Spaces, although not the Spaces you have"
" joined."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to nastavitev omogočena, sinhronizira vaše uporabniške podatke, Spaces"
" in ključe Space med napravami. Omogočanje tega povečuje vidnost "
"metapodatkov vašega računa, kar lahko razkrije, kdaj ste se pridružili novim"
" Spaces, čeprav ne tistim, ki ste se jim pridružili."

#: src/components/modals/SpaceSettingsModal/General.tsx:310
msgid ""
"When messages are signed, senders confirm they come from their key. When "
"messages aren't signed, senders have plausible deniability. This setting "
"applies to all messages in this Space."
msgstr ""
"Ko so sporočila podpisana, pošiljatelji potrjujejo, da prihajajo iz "
"njihovega ključa. Ko sporočila niso podpisana, imajo pošiljatelji verjetno "
"zanikanje. Ta nastavitev velja za vsa sporočila v tem prostoru."

#: src/components/modals/ConversationSettingsModal.tsx:244
msgid ""
"When muted, new messages won't show unread indicators or desktop "
"notifications."
msgstr ""
"Ko je utišano, nova sporočila ne bodo prikazovala neprebranih indikatorjev "
"ali namiznih obvestil."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:359
msgid ""
"When on, everyone in a space channel sees when you're typing, and you see "
"when they're typing."
msgstr ""
"Če je vklopljeno, vse v kanalu prostora vidijo, ko pišete, in vidite, ko "
"pišejo."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:288
msgid ""
"When on, senders see when their messages reach your device, and you see when"
" yours reach theirs."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljeno, pošiljatelji vidijo, kdaj njihova sporočila dosežejo vašo "
"napravo, vi pa vidite, kdaj vaša dosežejo njihovo."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:312
msgid ""
"When on, senders see when you've read their messages, and you see when yours"
" are read."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljeno, pošiljatelji vidijo, kdaj preberete njihova sporočila, vi "
"pa vidite, kdaj so vaša prebrana."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:382
msgid ""
"When on, your device fetches thumbnails from YouTube for the links you send,"
" which reveals your IP to Google. When off, recipients see a plain link "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljeno, vaše napravo pridobi slike z YouTube-a za povezave, ki jih"
" pošiljate, kar razkrije vaš IP naslov Google-u. Ko je izklopljeno, "
"prejemniki vidijo običajno povezavo namesto tega."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:336
msgid ""
"When on, your DM contacts see when you're typing, and you see when they're "
"typing."
msgstr ""
"Če je vklopljeno, vaši stikovniki v zasebnih sporočilih vidijo, ko pišete, "
"in vidite, ko pišejo."

